            Create single entry within the archive.

      The name of the entry.
      The fully qualified name of the new file, or the relative file name to be compressed.
      True if open the file immediately, otherwise open the file on archive saving.
      Compression and encryption settings used for added  item.
      Zip entry instance.


The entry name is solely set within  parameter. The file name provided in  parameter does not affect the entry name.

If the file is opened immediately with  parameter it becomes blocked until archive is saved.

